  "description": "Juicy sausages. Creamy mash. Onion marmalade? Not your regular trio, we know. It's onion marmalade that gives your gravy a rich tang, bringing this British comfort classic to life. Vibrant green beans and oven-roasted carrots make it bursting with goodness too!",
